Notes &quot;[[The cult of speed]]&quot;
coined by journalist Carl Honore Fast and slow are shorthand for ==ways of being, or philosophies of life== Fast: busy, controlling, aggressive, hurried, analytical, stressed, superficial, impatient, active, quantity-over-quality Slow: calm, careful, receptive, still, intuitive, unhurried, patient, reflective, quality-over-quantity.
